This paper focuses on the management of IoT devices through automatic cross-device classification by analyzing network traffic. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the potential for enhanced security, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The proposed method uses machine learning techniques, specifically LSTM-CNN, which suggests a possible fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also presents experimental results, indicating a potential fit for cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the potential extensions and applications of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
